@startuml
title State diagram for the Online Quiz System

state "Unregistered" as Unregistered
state "Registered" as Registered
state "Login" as Login
state "Teacher Home" as TeacherHome
state "Student Home" as StudentHome
state "Create Quiz" as CreateQuiz
state "Edit Quiz" as EditQuiz
state "Save Quiz" as SaveQuiz
state "Post Quiz" as PostQuiz
state "View Quiz Results" as ViewQuizResults
state "Select Quiz" as SelectQuiz
state "Answer Quiz" as AnswerQuiz
state "Submit Quiz" as SubmitQuiz
state "View Quiz Result" as ViewQuizResult
state "Logged Out" as LoggedOut

[*] --> Unregistered

Unregistered --> Registered : Register
Registered --> Login : Login

Login --> TeacherHome : Continue as Teacher
Login --> StudentHome : Continue as Student
TeacherHome --> CreateQuiz : Create Quiz
TeacherHome --> EditQuiz : Edit Quiz
TeacherHome --> SaveQuiz : Save Quiz
TeacherHome --> PostQuiz : Post Quiz
TeacherHome --> ViewQuizResults : View Quiz Results
StudentHome --> SelectQuiz : Select Quiz
SelectQuiz --> AnswerQuiz : Answer Quiz
AnswerQuiz --> SubmitQuiz : Submit Quiz
SubmitQuiz --> ViewQuizResult : View Quiz Result
ViewQuizResult --> StudentHome : Return to Home
ViewQuizResults --> TeacherHome : Return to Home
LoggedOut --> [*]

@enduml
